Unfortunately I didn't finish my personal website by the 25th which was the original deadline. I anticipated getting more done last weekend, but I ended up doing more errands and being a bit lazier than expected.

As a result the new deadline is this Monday, December 2nd 2019. I'm gonna work on it this weekend and however much is done will be released. I'm getting to the point where there are other projects I want to work on, so I'm gonna deliver a minimum viable product and update it at some point in the future.

I intend on putting together a basic resume page, if theres time I will also put together a basic About Me page. I don't think I'll get to the point where I can put pictures in the blog posts but I'm okay with that being a later update.

While the color scheme of the site isn't perfect, I like it enough to be delivered, so I won't be updating it for this release.
